@page
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "The Space";
}

<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="relative h-[72vh] flex items-end overflow-hidden">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518611012118-696072aa579a?q=80&w=2200" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" alt="Lumina studio space in Rondebosch with soft natural light and wooden floors">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none bg-gradient-to-b from-black/10 via-black/45 to-black/85"></div>
        <div class="relative px-6 pb-20 max-w-3xl text-white">
            <div class="uppercase tracking-[4px] text-xs mb-3 opacity-80">RONDEBOSCH • CAPE TOWN</div>
            <h1 class="text-7xl md:text-[78px] font-light tracking-[-3.2px] leading-none">The Space</h1>
            <p class="mt-5 text-2xl font-light tracking-tight max-w-lg">A light-filled sanctuary where clinical care and soulful movement live under one roof.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="px-6 py-16 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-16 gap-y-14">
        <div>
            <h2 class="text-5xl tracking-tighter font-light leading-none">Designed so you can finally arrive.</h2>
            <div class="mt-7 text-[17px] leading-relaxed text-lumina-charcoal/80 space-y-5 max-w-prose">
                <p>Every surface, every beam of light, every carefully chosen texture was chosen with one intention: helping you feel safe enough to soften.</p>
                <p>The reclaimed oak floors are warm under bare feet. Enormous windows frame the ancient oaks of Rondebosch. In the golden hours, the entire studio glows.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-9 pt-2">
            <div class="flex gap-5">
                <div class="w-9 h-9 mt-1 flex-shrink-0 text-3xl">🌿</div>
                <div>
                    <div class="font-medium text-lg tracking-tight">Biophilic by design</div>
                    <div class="text-lumina-charcoal/70 mt-1">Living plants, natural clay walls, and direct views into the garden. Your nervous system notices before your mind does.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-5">
                <div class="w-9 h-9 mt-1 flex-shrink-0 text-3xl">☀️</div>
                <div>
                    <div class="font-medium text-lg tracking-tight">Light as medicine</div>
                    <div class="text-lumina-charcoal/70 mt-1">Morning reformer bathed in clean eastern light. Restorative classes held in the honeyed glow of late afternoon.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-5">
                <div class="w-9 h-9 mt-1 flex-shrink-0 text-3xl">🤝</div>
                <div>
                    <div class="font-medium text-lg tracking-tight">Physio synergy, literally downstairs</div>
                    <div class="text-lumina-charcoal/70 mt-1">We share the building with exceptional physiotherapists. Referrals flow both ways. Your movement practice and your healing are never separated.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Immersive Gallery -->
    <div class="px-6 pb-16">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-12 gap-3 auto-rows-[minmax(180px,1fr)]">
            <div class="md:col-span-5 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden relative group">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544367567-0f2fcb009e0b?q=80&w=1100" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-[1.04] transition-transform duration-[850ms]" alt="Restorative circle in morning light">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
                <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 text-white text-sm tracking-wide">Restorative circle • early light</div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-4 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden relative group">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518611012118-696072aa579a?q=80&w=900" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-[1.04] transition-transform duration-[850ms]" alt="Reformer studio">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
                <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 text-white text-sm tracking-wide">The reformer room</div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-3 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden relative group">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506126613408-eca07ce68773?q=80&w=700" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-[1.04] transition-transform duration-[850ms]" alt="Quiet corner">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
                <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 text-white text-sm tracking-wide">The quiet corner</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="md:col-span-4 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden relative group">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544367567-0f2fcb009e0b?q=80&w=900" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-[1.04] transition-transform duration-[850ms]" alt="Props and care">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
                <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 text-white text-sm tracking-wide">Abundant, beautiful props</div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-8 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden relative group">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518611012118-696072aa579a?q=80&w=1600" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-[1.04] transition-transform duration-[850ms]" alt="Community after class">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
                <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 text-white">
                    <div class="text-sm tracking-wide">Tea and conversation on the deck after Saturday class</div>
                    <div class="text-xs opacity-70 mt-0.5">This is where the real community lives</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="px-6 pb-20 text-center">
        <div class="max-w-md mx-auto text-lumina-charcoal/70 text-[15px]">
            The space was never meant to impress. It was meant to disappear — so all that remains is you, your breath, and the quiet power of moving with presence.
        </div>
    </div>
</div>